newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,827 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,827 contracts.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 1,827 contracts compared with 1,599 overnight Monday.
There were 45 wheat, 752 corn, 848 soybean, 83 soymeal, 25 soyoil, two oat, one corn call, 33 soybean calls and 38 soybean puts traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was steady to 1-1/2 cents higher, corn was 1/4 to 3/4 cent lower and soybeans were 1-1/2 to 6-1/2 cents higher.
